c1 s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng l\u1edbn<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mo-thay-khung-long\/#Loi_ket\" >L\u1eddi k\u1ebft\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mo-thay-khung-long\/\">M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long<\/a> l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o l\u00e0nh hay d\u1eef? N\u00f3 d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai? N\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i may m\u1eafn? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m khi n\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con kh\u1ee7ng long. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i SV368<\/a> s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p chi ti\u1ebft, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi nh\u00e9.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Luan_giai_chi_tiet_ve_giac_mo_thay_khung_long\"><\/span><b>Lu\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u1ee7ng long l\u00e0 lo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n s\u00e2u v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1m th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con kh\u1ee7ng long l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o l\u00e0nh hay d\u1eef th\u00ec ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i x\u00e9t chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ng\u1eef c\u1ea3nh li\u00ean quan. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p<\/span><b> m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nam_mo_thay_con_khung_long\"><\/span><b>N\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con kh\u1ee7ng long<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chi\u00eam bao th\u1ea5y con kh\u1ee7ng long chung chung ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u1edf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1c h\u1eadu, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 sai l\u1ea7m v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u00e3y h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u00fang. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n, b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3770\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3770\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3770\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-1.jpg\" alt=\"Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-1.jpg?v=1735818235 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-1-300x169.jpg?v=1735818235 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-1-768x432.jpg?v=1735818235 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3770\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chiem_bao_thay_khung_long_bay\"><\/span><b>Chi\u00eam bao th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long bay<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu trong gi\u1ea5c <\/span><b>m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111ang bay th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sai l\u1ea7m. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n \u0111i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc th\u00eam c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vi\u1ec7c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng th\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n n\u00ean xem x\u00e9t th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nam_mo_thay_khung_long_bao_chua\"><\/span><b>N\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long b\u1ea1o ch\u00faa<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u1ee7 m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con kh\u1ee7ng long b\u1ea1o ch\u00faa th\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00ean c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng. Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o b\u1edfi s\u1ee3 lo l\u1eafng, khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p cho nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n, b\u1ea1n b\u00e8.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3769\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3769\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3769\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-2.jpg\" alt=\"Chi\u00eam bao th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long b\u1ea1o ch\u00faa\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-2.jpg?v=1735818235 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-2-300x169.jpg?v=1735818235 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-2-768x432.jpg?v=1735818235 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3769\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chi\u00eam bao th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long b\u1ea1o ch\u00faa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chiem_bao_thay_ban_than_dang_giet_khung_long\"><\/span><b>Chi\u00eam bao th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111ang gi\u1ebft kh\u1ee7ng long<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111ang gi\u1ebft con kh\u1ee7ng long th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n m\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t trong th\u1eddi gian qua. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u00f2n b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec1u hanh th\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mong_thay_khung_long_danh_nhau\"><\/span><b>M\u1ed9ng th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111\u00e1nh nhau<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y hai con kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111\u00e1nh nhau th\u00ec h\u00e3y c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn trong chuy\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ai \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec n\u00ean c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111ang che gi\u1ea5u b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh th\u00ec h\u00e3y ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi m\u1eb9 ch\u1ed3ng n\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf n\u00ean nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi n\u00f3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 hai c\u00f9ng m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3768\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3768\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3768\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-3.jpg\" alt=\"Lu\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i chi\u00eam bao th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111\u00e1nh nhau\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-3.jpg?v=1735818234 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-3-300x169.jpg?v=1735818234 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-3-768x432.jpg?v=1735818234 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3768\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Lu\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i chi\u00eam bao th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111\u00e1nh nhau<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nam_mo_thay_xuong_khung_long\"><\/span><b>N\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y x\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng long<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u1ee7 m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y x\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng long l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o t\u1ed1t, cho th\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh y\u00eau \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. H\u00e3y m\u1edf l\u00f2ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nam_mo_thay_khung_long_danh_de_so_may_de_thang_lon\"><\/span><b>N\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng l\u1edbn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o \u1edf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai th\u00ec gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con kh\u1ee7ng long c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 may m\u1eafn cho c\u00e1c l\u00f4 th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm v\u1eadn may c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u1ee7<\/span><b> m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> b\u1ea1o ch\u00faa h\u00e3y \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 05 &#8211; 97.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9ng th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111ang sinh con h\u00e3y phang ngay c\u1eb7p s\u1ed1 12 &#8211; 43.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111ang \u0103n c\u1ecf th\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 68 &#8211; 80.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y hai con kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111\u00e1nh nhau th\u00ec h\u00e3y th\u1eed v\u1eadn may v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p l\u00f4 26 &#8211; 75.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng con kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111ang bay l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 15 &#8211; 55.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9ng th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long b\u1ecb gi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh ngay c\u1eb7p s\u1ed1 19 &#8211; 38.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u1ee7 m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng long r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 14 &#8211; 46.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e0n kh\u1ee7ng long v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0u n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 91 &#8211; 33.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0103n th\u1ecbt m\u00ecnh th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng b\u1ecf qua s\u1ed1 35 &#8211; 66.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n kh\u1ee7ng long n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 35 &#8211; 61.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u1ee7 m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con kh\u1ee7ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea3y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e1u l\u00e0 s\u1ed1\u00a0 25 &#8211; 31.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chi\u00eam bao th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u0111i s\u0103n kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 01 &#8211; 22.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3767\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3767\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3767\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-4.jpg\" alt=\"N\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-4.jpg?v=1735818234 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-4-300x169.jpg?v=1735818234 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/mo-thay-khung-long-4-768x432.jpg?v=1735818234 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3767\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">N\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long \u0111\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Loi_ket\"><\/span><b>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean SV368 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p <\/span><b>m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 may m\u1eafn \u0111i k\u00e8m. Hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 m\u00ecnh g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm v\u1eadn may th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ee3i \u00fd ph\u00eda tr\u00ean nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u01a1 th\u1ea5y kh\u1ee7ng long l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o l\u00e0nh hay d\u1eef? N\u00f3 d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai? N\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 m\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i may m\u1eafn? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m khi n\u1eb1m m\u01a1 th\u1ea5y con kh\u1ee7ng long. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e0 [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3770,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[7],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3766","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xo-so"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3766","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3766"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3766\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5913,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3766\/revisions\/5913"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3770"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/